After the three pigs get kicked out from their household they go to the shopkeeper and the shopkeeper asks them what they want. The youngest one wanted straw. The middle pig wanted sticks. The oldest pig wanted bricks. They youngest pig constructed his house the quickest, followed by the middle pig and the oldest pig constructed his house last. After all this occured, a big, bad , wolf appeared and made his way to the youngest pig's house, he then blew the house down. 

